Package org.hiphap

Class Organization

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hiphap.Entity
      • org.hiphap.Organization
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, CsvPrintable
    public class Organization
extends Entity
    This class represents an organization that the system keeps track of, making it easier for it to be reused under several different events. It inherits from the abstract Entity base class, adding further attributes and behaviour.
